components.name: Extract Claims CSV
components.description: Reads claims.csv from the local filesystem and pushes the extracted records via XCom for downstream processing.

connections.purpose: Read CSV files from local disk

components.name: Extract Providers CSV
components.description: Reads providers.csv from the local filesystem and pushes the extracted records via XCom for downstream processing.

connections.purpose: Read CSV files from local disk

components.name: Join and Anonymize Claims with Providers
components.description: Joins extracted claims and provider data, anonymizes PII, and calculates risk scores, producing a transformed dataset for loading.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after both extraction tasks have succeeded.

components.name: Load Transformed Data to Data Warehouse
components.description: Writes the transformed claims and provider data into the healthcare_analytics Postgres warehouse tables.

upstream_policy.description: Executes after the transform_join task completes successfully.

connections.purpose: Write transformed data to Postgres analytics warehouse

components.name: Refresh BI Dashboards
components.description: Triggers refresh of Power BI and Tableau dashboards after data is loaded into the warehouse.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after the transform_join task completes successfully, in parallel with load_warehouse.
